                            Bank A says "Starbucks Coffee", Bank B says "TST*Starbucks 022". 
                            You need a robust categorization engine.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-200 p-4 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono overflow-x-auto">
                            // Logic Pseudocode<br>
                            const transaction = await BankAPI.getTrans();<br>
                            const category = TaxEngine.classify(transaction.merchant);<br>
                            if (category.isDeductible) {<br>
                              &nbsp;&nbsp;TaxSavings.add(transaction.amount * taxRate);<br>
                            }<br>
                        </div>
                    </div>

