                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                         <div class="w-64 flex-shrink-0">
                            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-2">PHASE 2 (Months 4-6)</div>
                            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-teal-600 shadow-sm h-full">
