                                    <li>‚Ä¢ Validate "Auto-Categorization"</li>
                                    <li>‚Ä¢ Fix API connection bugs</li>
                                    <li>‚Ä¢ Security Audit (Basic)</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                         <div class="w-64 flex-shrink-0">
                            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-2">PHASE 3 (Months 7-12)</div>
